The REDiMED Doctor is an independent Doctor who has been requested by my employer/insurance company to assess my fitness to work. I understand that the REDiMED Doctor will not be treating me but is undertaking an assessment of my fitness to work and may make recommendations regarding my fitness for full duty employment, as described by my employer/insurance company.

I understand that the assessment is intended to cover all aspects of health that may interact with my ability to work. I understand the information I discuss that is considered relevant, will be included in the report.

I understand that there may be a physical examination component to the assessment. I understand that it is my responsibility to advise immediately if I experience any difficulties during the examination process.

I understand that the medical recommendations and report will be made available to my employer/insurance company. Should I wish to request a copy of the report, I understand that I will need to request this from the company that has requested the fitness to work examination. I acknowledge I will not be able to access this via the REDiMED Doctor.

I further understand that if I do not sign all consents below to release information then the fitness for work examination may not proceed. I have read and understand the information regarding the fitness for work assessment and give full consent to proceed.
